title: Column icons don't show up in connecting Derby database
OB: When expanding the Data Source in the Available Items sector by clicking the related icon, the table icons are displayed but the column icons are not.
EB: Expected behavior is that both the table icons and column icons are displayed when expanding the Data Source.
SR: Steps to reproduce: 1. Open the application and navigate to the Available Items sector. 2. Click on the icon related to the Data Source. 3. Observe that the table icons are displayed but the column icons are missing.
